Package CAMs_App.data

Class Database

java.lang.Object
CAMs_App.data.Database
public class Database extends Object
The Database class manages the data storage within the application. It offers methods to get and set the data maps for different data types, as well as calling methods from DatabaseService for import and export data to and from the file system.
